            <p>danh s√°ch c√°c ƒë·ªÅ xu·∫•t ƒëang ch·ªù duy·ªát s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c hi·ªÉn th·ªã ·ªü ƒë√¢y.</p>
            {/* Placeholder for the list of proposals */}
            <ListGroup style={{ maxHeight: "450px", overflowY: "auto" }}>
